                    </td>
                    <td colspan="1" class="text-left">
                        <span>公斤</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>食味值：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="3">
                        <span t-field="doc.TasteRating"></span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="1" class="text-left">
                        <span>分</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>穀重：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="3">
                        <span t-field="doc.CropWeight"></span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="1" class="text-left">
                        <span>公斤</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>糙米完整率：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="3">
                        <span t-field="doc.BrownIntactRatio"></span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="1" class="text-left">
                        <span>%</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>乾穀重量：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="9">
                        <span t-field="doc.CropWeight"></span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="1" class="text-left">
                        <span>公斤</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>備註欄：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="4">
                        <span></span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>經收人：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="4">
                        <span></span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="6" rowspan="2" class="align-middle">
                        <span>
                            池上多力米股份有限公司
                            <br />
                            /建興碾米工廠
                        </span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="6" class="text-left">
                        <span>台東縣池上鄉中山路193-1號1樓</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="3" class="text-left">
                        <span>電話： 089861033</span>
